1
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,519
He was supposed to be on duty yesterday.

2
00:01:51,519 --> 00:01:52,439
Shift change was at six.

3
00:01:52,719 --> 00:01:53,719
It was almost time.

4
00:01:53,719 --> 00:01:55,400
He called and said he had something to do.

5
00:01:56,319 --> 00:01:58,159
I found someone to cover for him at the last minute.

6
00:01:58,159 --> 00:01:59,319
Did he say what it was about?

7
00:01:59,519 --> 00:02:00,319
No, he didn't.

8
00:02:00,439 --> 00:02:01,920
Do you have a copy of his ID?

9
00:02:03,599 --> 00:02:05,439
You hired him without even having his ID?

10
00:02:05,439 --> 00:02:06,359
No, that's not it, man.

11
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:08,039
You can't blame me for this.

12
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:10,840
He said he lost his ID and is getting a new one.

13
00:02:10,879 --> 00:02:13,080
I got so busy that I forgot about it.

14
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:13,879
I already asked.

15
00:02:13,879 --> 00:02:16,520
His name is Yang Jian, "Jian" as in "inspect."

16
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:18,080
Right, I also have his...

17
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:19,360
...handwritten home address.

18
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:19,879
I'll find it for you.

19
00:02:19,879 --> 00:02:20,759
Hurry, find it.

20
00:02:24,759 --> 00:02:25,639
Here it is, bro.

21
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:28,520
How much do you pay him per month?

22
00:02:28,719 --> 00:02:29,919
I pay him eighteen hundred.

23
00:02:30,319 --> 00:02:31,639
But I also heard

24
00:02:31,639 --> 00:02:33,000
they secretly sell some stuff here.

25
00:02:33,159 --> 00:02:34,639
Cigarettes, drinks, instant noodles.

26
00:02:34,639 --> 00:02:35,639
Just to make some pocket money.

27
00:02:35,719 --> 00:02:36,639
I know all about that.

28
00:02:36,639 --> 00:02:37,759
I can't be bothered to deal with him.

29
00:02:37,879 --> 00:02:39,639
As long as he keeps the accounts straight for me,

30
00:02:39,639 --> 00:02:40,400
I'm fine with whatever.

31
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:43,120
Who is he usually close with?

32
00:02:43,639 --> 00:02:44,680
That I don't know.

33
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:46,639
Is there anyone who comes to see him often?

34
00:02:47,039 --> 00:02:48,639
He has a little girlfriend.

35
00:02:48,719 --> 00:02:50,120
I heard she's still in school.

36
00:02:50,639 --> 00:02:51,639
Sometimes she comes here to use the internet.

37
00:02:51,639 --> 00:02:52,800
The two of them play games together.

38
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:53,639
What's her name?

39
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:55,639
I saw her just a couple of days ago.

40
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:57,919
Her name is Tang... Tang something.

41
00:02:57,919 --> 00:02:58,960
Let me check for you, bro.

42
00:02:58,960 --> 00:02:59,520
I'll look for you.

43
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,039
I'll look for you.

44
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:01,840
Tang, Tang Jian Yong.

45
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:02,759
Do you know Yang Jian?

46
00:03:03,039 --> 00:03:03,840
Yeah, I know him.

47
00:03:04,039 --> 00:03:05,639
Was he killed by someone?

48
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:07,159
How do you know he was killed?

49
00:03:07,159 --> 00:03:08,719
Everyone in our guild knows.

50
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,639
They even sent out a notice.

51
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:11,639
What guild?

52
00:03:11,639 --> 00:03:12,840
The gaming guild.

53
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,400
We all publicly mourned him.

54
00:03:14,439 --> 00:03:16,240
But that woman didn't even say a word.

55
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,639
Wait, which woman?

56
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,800
Tang Jianyong.

57
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:20,120
Her online name is Princess Xiangxiang.

58
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,039
Her.

59
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:23,080
And Yang Jian was so good to her.

60
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:25,000
He helped her level up and clear maps every day.

61
00:03:25,639 --> 00:03:26,840
He was really blind.

62
00:03:27,039 --> 00:03:28,319
Are you friends with Yang Jian?

63
00:03:29,639 --> 00:03:30,919
Not exactly.

64
00:03:32,039 --> 00:03:34,240
Anyway, he was really impressive in the group.

65
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:36,319
We all admired him.

66
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,680
I even reached out to him before.

67
00:03:37,719 --> 00:03:38,919
Asked him to help me out.

68
00:03:39,159 --> 00:03:41,000
But he ignored me because of that woman.

69
00:03:41,319 --> 00:03:43,639
Do you know this Princess Xiangxiang?

70
00:03:43,639 --> 00:03:44,520
Yeah, I know her.

71
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,719
Everyone in the group knows her.

72
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:47,000
She has two boyfriends.

73
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,080
One is Yang Jian.

74
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:49,680
The other one spends money on her.

75
00:03:51,919 --> 00:03:52,919
I guess,

76
00:03:52,919 --> 00:03:54,360
it was that man who killed him.

77
00:03:57,199 --> 00:03:58,759
Then who is this man?

78
00:03:58,759 --> 00:03:59,680
Do you know him?

79
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:00,960
His name is Luo Bo.

80
00:04:02,159 --> 00:04:03,719
He owns a building materials store.

81
00:04:03,719 --> 00:04:04,919
Which "Luo"? Which "Bo"?

82
00:04:05,159 --> 00:04:06,159
The "Luo" from the surname Luo.

83
00:04:06,759 --> 00:04:07,400
The "Bo" from "waves."

84
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,199
What are you here for?

85
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:31,000
What are you here for?

86
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:31,720
Hello.

87
00:04:31,959 --> 00:04:33,959
Um, is this place closed down?

88
00:04:33,959 --> 00:04:34,639
Has it been transferred?

89
00:04:34,639 --> 00:04:36,639
No, it's not closed, just taking a break for a couple of days.

90
00:04:36,639 --> 00:04:38,879
So it's just closed for these two days, right? Yes, that's right.

91
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:41,839
We also want to rent a place nearby.

92
00:04:41,839 --> 00:04:42,639
So we wanted to take a look.

93
00:04:42,639 --> 00:04:44,040
If they're transferring, we want to rent it.

94
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:45,439
Are your two units the same layout?

95
00:04:45,439 --> 00:04:46,360
They're about the same size.

96
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:47,439
Can we take a look?

97
00:04:47,439 --> 00:04:48,240
Sure, come on.

98
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:48,720
Thank you.

99
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,480
No problem.

100
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:57,319
No one lives here, right?

101
00:04:57,519 --> 00:04:59,000
No one lives in mine, but someone lives in theirs.

102
00:04:59,279 --> 00:04:59,680
They've always lived there.

103
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:01,120
Yeah, I saw that someone lives there.

104
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:02,639
Right, they've always been living inside.

105
00:05:02,639 --> 00:05:03,639
They've always lived here?

106
00:05:03,639 --> 00:05:04,480
Yes, yes, yes.

107
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:05,639
This way, you can save some money.

108
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:10,720
When was the last time you saw him come back?

109
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,399
I haven't seen him these past couple of days anyway.

110
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,560
He hasn't opened the door these past two days either.

111
00:05:15,319 --> 00:05:16,639
Are you two close?

112
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:19,079
We're just neighbors who do business.

113
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:23,040
Did you know Yang Jian was killed?

114
00:05:23,959 --> 00:05:24,759
Yeah, I know.

115
00:05:25,399 --> 00:05:26,519
Aren't you scared?

116
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:28,720
Scared of what?

117
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,800
It's not like I killed him.

118
00:05:31,279 --> 00:05:32,199
He had it coming.

119
00:05:33,079 --> 00:05:34,199
Why did he have it coming?

120
00:05:34,519 --> 00:05:35,160
No, that's not it—

121
00:05:35,399 --> 00:05:35,959
Ziming.

122
00:05:37,399 --> 00:05:38,560
Ask a bit slower.

123
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:39,759
I can't keep up.

124
00:05:39,759 --> 00:05:40,560
Let me do it.

125
00:05:41,079 --> 00:05:41,879
Alright.

126
00:05:48,319 --> 00:05:49,839
How did you meet Yang Jian?

127
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:52,120
We met last year while playing games.

128
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:54,920
He was really good in the game.

129
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,560
If he didn't like someone, he'd just attack them.

130
00:05:57,319 --> 00:05:59,040
He also had a nice voice.

131
00:05:59,839 --> 00:06:01,680
He sounded pretty cool.

132
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,720
But when I saw him, I didn't feel anything.

133
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,040
Later on,

134
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:07,040
he kept calling me.

135
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:08,959
He even helped me level up in the game.

136
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,839
I thought he was pretty good to me.

137
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:12,439
So we got together.

138
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:16,279
So how did you meet Luo Bo?

139
00:06:17,279 --> 00:06:18,120
Tell us.

140
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:19,319
What's going on?

141
00:06:19,759 --> 00:06:21,439
How do you guys know everything?

142
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,480
Just answer what we ask.

143
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:24,680
How did you meet?

144
00:06:24,959 --> 00:06:26,639
We met at a mixer.

145
00:06:26,839 --> 00:06:27,920
He pursued me.

146
00:06:28,279 --> 00:06:29,879
He was pretty good to me too.

147
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:32,319
It's a genuine kind of kindness.

148
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:34,120
What do you mean by "genuine" kindness?

149
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:36,680
Give me money to spend.

150
00:06:37,279 --> 00:06:39,680
Someone saw you go to Yang Jian's house last week.

151
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:41,279
You even went to the internet cafe to look for him.

152
00:06:42,199 --> 00:06:43,040
Is that true?

153
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,079
Yes.

154
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:45,680
Why did you go to see him?

155
00:06:46,199 --> 00:06:48,199
Luo Bo is nice to me, that's true.

156
00:06:48,639 --> 00:06:50,920
But we just can't have a good conversation.

157
00:06:51,399 --> 00:06:54,720
Yang Jian doesn't even log into his own account every day.

158
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,360
He just helps me keep my account online.

159
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:58,360
So I was a little touched.

160
00:06:58,759 --> 00:06:59,720
You were really touched?

161
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:02,240
If you were really touched, why did you say he deserved to die?

162
00:07:02,879 --> 00:07:05,759
You even went to Yang Jian's house the day before the incident.

163
00:07:05,959 --> 00:07:07,839
Can you really say his death has nothing to do with you?

164
00:07:08,759 --> 00:07:10,279
It really has nothing to do with me.

165
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:12,279
If that's true, then why did you go to his house?

166
00:07:12,279 --> 00:07:13,720
I went to ask him for money.

167
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:14,959
What money?

168
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:19,279
I'm asking you, what money do you want?

169
00:07:19,279 --> 00:07:20,480
Why do you want money?

170
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:21,480
Money for medical treatment.

171
00:07:22,199 --> 00:07:23,000
Are you satisfied now?

172
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:24,279
What illness are you talking about?

173
00:07:25,759 --> 00:07:26,800
You tell me, what illness?

174
00:07:26,879 --> 00:07:29,480
Why are you asking him for money for your treatment?

175
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:30,639
He infected me.

176
00:07:30,639 --> 00:07:32,079
If I don't ask him, who else should I ask?

177
00:07:32,279 --> 00:07:33,600
Has Luo Bo contacted you recently?

178
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:34,480
No.

179
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:36,480
I've called him several times.

180
00:07:36,959 --> 00:07:37,759
He didn't answer.

181
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:44,199
You don't really think it was Luo Bo who did it, do you?

182
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,279
Call him right now.

183
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:48,680
No way.

184
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:52,279
The two of them got along pretty well.

185
00:07:52,279 --> 00:07:53,600
Like brothers.

186
00:07:54,199 --> 00:07:56,439
Then who do you think is most likely?

187
00:07:57,319 --> 00:07:59,560
Who knows what kind of shady people he got involved with.

188
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:05,480
I can't get through.

189
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,879
Maybe I should just leave the phone with you.

190
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:14,199
Luo Bo is now a key suspect.

191
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,360
No matter how he contacts you,

192
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:18,279
you must inform the police immediately.

193
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:19,720
Thank you for your cooperation.

194
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,839
Come, handle the necessary procedures with me.

195
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,879
Don't break my phone.

196
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:26,360
Remember to return it to me when you're done.

197
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:36,879
Sorry

198
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:39,840
The number you have dialed is temporarily unavailable

199
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,399
Please try again later

200
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,919
What do you think of Luo Bo?

201
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:01,480
He's a pretty good guy.

202
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:03,399
He can endure hardship and is loyal.

203
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,840
But about his girlfriend...

204
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:06,320
We don't think she's that great.

205
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,399
What's his girlfriend's name?

206
00:09:07,399 --> 00:09:09,159
Her name is Tang Jianyong.

207
00:09:09,799 --> 00:09:10,720
She's quite tall.

208
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:13,039
We often see her playing games.

209
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:14,519
She doesn't really help him with anything.

210
00:09:15,159 --> 00:09:18,639
He said all the money he's earned these past years has been spent on her.

211
00:09:18,799 --> 00:09:20,159
If Luo Bo contacts you,

212
00:09:20,639 --> 00:09:21,879
please remember to let us know.

213
00:09:21,879 --> 00:09:22,320
Okay.

214
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:23,600
Can I have your phone number?

215
00:09:39,399 --> 00:09:41,399
Stop messing with it. It's been broken for a long time.

216
00:09:42,639 --> 00:09:45,320
Why can't this one be fixed?

217
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,480
Hey, are you asleep?

218
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:03,080
Hello?

219
00:10:03,559 --> 00:10:04,320
Where is Tang Jian Yong?

220
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:06,039
Who are you? She's taking a shower.

221
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,480
I'm answering for her.

222
00:10:08,919 --> 00:10:09,759
Who are you?

223
00:10:10,919 --> 00:10:11,960
Who are you?

224
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:12,919
I'm her boyfriend.

225
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:14,159
I'm her boyfriend.

226
00:10:14,159 --> 00:10:14,879
Let her answer the phone.

227
00:10:15,159 --> 00:10:16,480
She's taking a shower. Are you deaf?

228
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,320
I already told you.

229
00:10:17,799 --> 00:10:18,519
Who are you?

230
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:19,720
Why is she showering?

231
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:20,720
Who are you, really?

232
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:21,559
Where are you two?

233
00:10:21,559 --> 00:10:23,399
I'm at her place. What's up?

234
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,519
Fine, fine.

235
00:10:24,519 --> 00:10:25,080
Just you wait.

236
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:26,799
I'll wait for you. I'm not scared.

237
00:10:31,399 --> 00:10:32,679
Backup will arrive in twenty minutes.

238
00:10:33,919 --> 00:10:34,960
Let's head out first.

239
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:56,159
Slow down, slow down.

240
00:10:56,399 --> 00:10:57,559
I told you to drink less.

241
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:01,440
Slow down, slow down, slow down.

242
00:11:02,039 --> 00:11:02,919
Are you okay?

243
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:03,440
I'm fine.

244
00:11:10,679 --> 00:11:11,440
What are you doing?

245
00:11:11,679 --> 00:11:12,440
Police, what's going on?

246
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:12,919
Don't move.

247
00:11:12,919 --> 00:11:13,440
Who are you people?

248
00:11:13,559 --> 00:11:14,879
What's your name? What's your name?

249
00:11:14,879 --> 00:11:15,639
Who are you?

250
00:11:15,639 --> 00:11:16,679
Police, what's your name?

251
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:18,000
Speak. Don't move.

252
00:11:18,279 --> 00:11:19,360
Luo, Luo Bo.

253
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:23,639
That noon, I had a bit to drink.

254
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:25,720
The more I thought about it, the angrier I got.

255
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:29,320
I support her, and he just plays around.

256
00:11:30,799 --> 00:11:32,720
Normally, we even call each other brothers.

257
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:37,320
Then in the afternoon,

258
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:39,320
I bought some alcohol and food.

259
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:40,480
And took it to their place.

260
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:42,480
I wanted to have a talk with him.

261
00:11:46,399 --> 00:11:47,559
Brother, I came here today

262
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:49,120
to talk to you.

263
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:50,480
Whatever happened before,

264
00:11:51,039 --> 00:11:52,879
I'll just let it go.

265
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:54,320
But from now on,

266
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:56,000
stay away from our Tang Jian Yong.

267
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:59,639
Then he said something that really pissed me off.

268
00:11:59,919 --> 00:12:00,799
What did he say?

269
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:02,639
You think she really likes you?

270
00:12:04,639 --> 00:12:06,279
She likes your money.

271
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:14,320
Look at you, how old are you already?

272
00:12:15,559 --> 00:12:17,080
What do you have to compare with me?

273
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:18,360
And you still want to negotiate with me?

274
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:19,360
Are you even qualified?

275
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:28,120
I hit him a few times and then he stopped moving.

276
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:29,480
Besides hitting him with a dumbbell,

277
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:30,679
