553
00:26:43,799 --> 00:26:44,799
Ziming, stop arguing.

554
00:26:44,799 --> 00:26:46,599
There were indeed flaws in our handling of the case.

555
00:26:46,720 --> 00:26:48,480
You're leaving anyway, so you don't care.

556
00:26:51,559 --> 00:26:53,480
What's your attitude?

557
00:26:55,480 --> 00:26:56,279
Captain Huang.

558
00:26:57,480 --> 00:26:59,680
If you say I'm not competent at work, I accept that.

559
00:27:00,279 --> 00:27:02,200
If you say I'm not thorough in handling cases, I accept that too.

560
00:27:02,440 --> 00:27:03,799
You can say whatever you want.

561
00:27:04,400 --> 00:27:05,960
I work hard every day.

562
00:27:06,359 --> 00:27:07,720
But in the end, you say I'm negligent.

563
00:27:08,039 --> 00:27:09,839
If you put it that way, are you happy with it?

564
00:27:12,000 --> 00:27:12,799
What is it?

565
00:27:14,559 --> 00:27:15,960
You think you're the only one working hard, huh?

566
00:27:17,279 --> 00:27:18,079
Look around.

567
00:27:18,920 --> 00:27:20,720
Everyone out there is working hard.

568
00:27:22,519 --> 00:27:23,680
I'm not going to waste words with you.

569
00:27:23,759 --> 00:27:25,000
Let me just ask you one thing.

570
00:27:25,480 --> 00:27:27,359
Are you going to write this self-criticism or not?

571
00:27:27,359 --> 00:27:28,079
No, I won't.

572
00:27:29,599 --> 00:27:31,079
You say I have a problem with my work attitude.

573
00:27:31,079 --> 00:27:31,880
I don't accept that.

574
00:27:40,839 --> 00:27:41,480
Fine.

575
00:27:44,359 --> 00:27:45,559
You don't have to accept it.

576
00:27:46,400 --> 00:27:47,720
Alright, I accept it, okay?

577
00:27:48,920 --> 00:27:50,240
The way you look right now

578
00:27:51,000 --> 00:27:52,880
is no longer suitable for continuing to work.

579
00:27:53,079 --> 00:27:54,119
Starting today

580
00:27:54,319 --> 00:27:56,799
go home on leave and wait for further notice.

581
00:27:59,920 --> 00:28:00,480
Captain Huang

582
00:28:00,680 --> 00:28:01,400
Leave.

583
00:28:10,839 --> 00:28:12,319
When did you find out I was leaving?

584
00:28:17,200 --> 00:28:18,000
No.

585
00:28:18,680 --> 00:28:21,079
What do you mean, a farewell party?

586
00:28:22,000 --> 00:28:22,880
It's not that serious.

587
00:28:25,200 --> 00:28:26,440
It's a farewell for the two of us.

588
00:28:29,119 --> 00:28:29,759
The three of us.

589
00:28:32,000 --> 00:28:32,920
I'm switching to a desk job.

590
00:28:35,000 --> 00:28:35,640
Come on.

591
00:28:36,680 --> 00:28:37,279
Lei.

592
00:28:38,079 --> 00:28:39,400
I just don't get it.

593
00:28:39,559 --> 00:28:40,759
Why are you doing this?

594
00:28:45,839 --> 00:28:47,079
One day, I had a dream.

595
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:50,559
I dreamed I was in the sky.

596
00:28:50,599 --> 00:28:51,839
I saw my son.

597
00:28:55,400 --> 00:28:58,000
From the day my son was born,

598
00:28:59,319 --> 00:29:01,079
I knew this day would come.

599
00:29:04,279 --> 00:29:05,400
I knew it, yes,

600
00:29:09,160 --> 00:29:10,720
but I still couldn't accept it.

601
00:29:12,400 --> 00:29:13,640
The day my son passed away,

602
00:29:16,440 --> 00:29:17,200
at the hospital,

603
00:29:18,720 --> 00:29:20,440
my daughter-in-law was in the hallway,

604
00:29:22,359 --> 00:29:23,160
crying.

605
00:29:24,920 --> 00:29:27,640
Then family and friends gathered around her, comforting her.

606
00:29:30,279 --> 00:29:30,880
I

607
00:29:31,880 --> 00:29:33,519
just stood by and watched.

608
00:29:37,920 --> 00:29:39,440
I didn't dare take a single step forward.

609
00:29:40,920 --> 00:29:42,839
I felt like I wasn't part of this family.

610
00:29:49,279 --> 00:29:50,599
I owe both of them, mother and daughter.

611
00:29:58,400 --> 00:30:00,480
Then you should have at least told us in advance.

612
00:30:04,000 --> 00:30:05,480
I didn't dare to say anything.

613
00:30:08,680 --> 00:30:10,480
If I had told you, you definitely would have tried to talk me out of it.

614
00:30:12,440 --> 00:30:13,480
And if you tried to persuade me—

615
00:30:19,799 --> 00:30:20,839
I can't bear to leave.

616
00:30:25,119 --> 00:30:25,920
Alright.

617
00:30:27,240 --> 00:30:28,920
Don't talk about these sad things.

618
00:30:29,079 --> 00:30:29,920
From now on,

619
00:30:31,240 --> 00:30:33,440
if you want to eat or drink anything,

620
00:30:34,839 --> 00:30:35,640
just come here.

621
00:30:38,920 --> 00:30:40,359
I've taken over this place.

622
00:30:42,359 --> 00:30:45,759
We'll tidy up and open for business next month.

623
00:30:49,359 --> 00:30:50,440
Come on.

624
00:31:14,920 --> 00:31:15,559
Sister

625
00:31:21,920 --> 00:31:22,559
Sister

626
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:23,799
What's wrong?

627
00:31:24,319 --> 00:31:25,319
The doctor said it's a cerebral infarction.

628
00:31:25,319 --> 00:31:26,599
They're trying to save him inside.

629
00:31:26,720 --> 00:31:28,039
How could he suddenly have a stroke?

630
00:31:28,039 --> 00:31:29,920
He said he felt chest tightness when he woke up this morning.

631
00:31:29,920 --> 00:31:30,640
He was feeling a bit unwell.

632
00:31:30,880 --> 00:31:32,480
By noon, he was feeling cold all over.

633
00:31:32,480 --> 00:31:33,640
Then he suddenly fainted.

634
00:31:34,759 --> 00:31:35,839
Isn't it your fault?

635
00:31:36,720 --> 00:31:38,319
Blame me? What did I do?

636
00:31:38,519 --> 00:31:40,720
As soon as he heard you were forced to take leave by your boss,

637
00:31:40,759 --> 00:31:42,160
he hasn't slept well for a week.

638
00:31:44,160 --> 00:31:45,799
He must be happy about that, right?

639
00:31:47,559 --> 00:31:48,480
Look at the situation we're in.

640
00:31:48,480 --> 00:31:49,680
And you're still joking around.

641
00:31:49,759 --> 00:31:50,559
Are you even human?

642
00:31:51,319 --> 00:31:52,920
Why is he even worrying about this?

643
00:31:53,319 --> 00:31:55,200
My taking leave doesn't affect his sleep.

644
00:31:56,319 --> 00:31:57,720
Were you actually fired or not?

645
00:31:58,039 --> 00:31:59,279
Can you even keep this job anymore?

646
00:32:00,400 --> 00:32:01,920
How would I know right now?

647
00:32:14,319 --> 00:32:15,279
Doctor, how is it?

648
00:32:16,559 --> 00:32:17,519
The surgery went very well.

649
00:32:17,519 --> 00:32:18,319
We'll transfer to the intensive care unit first.

650
00:32:18,319 --> 00:32:19,079
We'll observe for a few days.

651
00:32:19,079 --> 00:32:21,039
Once the condition stabilizes, we'll move to a regular ward.

652
00:32:21,319 --> 00:32:21,720
Okay, okay, take it slow.

653
00:32:21,720 --> 00:32:22,480
Thank you, thank you.

654
00:32:22,480 --> 00:32:23,200
Be careful.

655
00:32:28,839 --> 00:32:29,640
Let me do it.

656
00:32:29,720 --> 00:32:30,759
What do you mean, you'll do it?

657
00:32:30,759 --> 00:32:31,319
Can you afford it?

658
00:32:31,319 --> 00:32:32,200
It's tens of thousands.

659
00:32:32,519 --> 00:32:33,319
It's that expensive?

660
00:32:33,960 --> 00:32:34,759
Then you do it.

661
00:32:36,319 --> 00:32:37,519
Stop making me worry so much.

662
00:32:37,519 --> 00:32:38,319
Go focus on your work.

663
00:32:38,319 --> 00:32:39,119
Go to work if you should be working.

664
00:32:39,119 --> 00:32:39,880
Did you hear me?

665
00:32:40,680 --> 00:32:42,319
It's not up to me, either.

666
00:32:42,319 --> 00:32:43,480
We have to listen to the boss.

667
00:32:43,799 --> 00:32:44,960
So what are you planning to do?

668
00:32:45,240 --> 00:32:46,480
Just sleep at home all day?

669
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:50,559
How about this: when Dad gets a bit better,

670
00:32:51,440 --> 00:32:53,160
I'll ask my brother-in-law to lend me a car.

671
00:32:53,400 --> 00:32:54,480
I'll drive an unlicensed cab.

672
00:32:54,920 --> 00:32:56,119
Are you kidding me?

673
00:32:56,400 --> 00:32:57,319
I'm not kidding.

674
00:32:58,079 --> 00:33:00,039
I think you're really bored out of your mind right now.

675
00:33:17,759 --> 00:33:18,559
How are you doing?

676
00:33:18,559 --> 00:33:19,519
You're recovering well.

677
00:33:19,519 --> 00:33:20,440
You've been moved to a regular ward.

678
00:33:20,440 --> 00:33:21,519
Okay, let them take you.

679
00:33:21,559 --> 00:33:22,599
Alright, thank you, thank you.

680
00:33:24,200 --> 00:33:25,400
Why are you here?

681
00:33:26,000 --> 00:33:27,160
I'm here to take care of you.

682
00:33:28,000 --> 00:33:29,400
You don't need to take care of me so much.

683
00:33:29,599 --> 00:33:31,119
I can still live for another two years.

684
00:33:31,680 --> 00:33:33,039
Stop talking so much.

685
00:33:42,519 --> 00:33:44,440
You have to at least tell me why you called me here.

686
00:33:44,440 --> 00:33:45,319
It's a good thing.

687
00:33:45,799 --> 00:33:47,079
What good thing could it be?

688
00:33:47,119 --> 00:33:48,319
You'll know when you get there.

689
00:33:49,359 --> 00:33:50,119
Come on, come on.

690
00:33:50,599 --> 00:33:51,240
Um...

691
00:33:51,920 --> 00:33:53,079
This is the person I told you about.

692
00:33:53,079 --> 00:33:54,000
My brother-in-law. Hello.

693
00:33:54,000 --> 00:33:54,799
Liu Ziming.

694
00:33:55,079 --> 00:33:56,359
Help him with the onboarding procedures.

695
00:33:56,359 --> 00:33:57,559
He used to be a detective.

696
00:33:57,720 --> 00:33:58,960
The contract is all ready.

697
00:33:58,960 --> 00:33:59,720
Please take a look.

698
00:33:59,839 --> 00:33:59,880
Wait, what contract am I signing?

699
00:33:59,880 --> 00:34:01,319
Wait, what contract am I signing?

700
00:34:01,720 --> 00:34:02,559
From now on,

701
00:34:02,559 --> 00:34:04,359
you're my personal assistant.

702
00:34:04,839 --> 00:34:07,000
In this company, you're second only to me.

703
00:34:08,719 --> 00:34:10,920
What does a personal assistant even do?

704
00:34:10,920 --> 00:34:11,719
You...

705
00:34:11,880 --> 00:34:14,239
With our resources, we can do anything.

706
00:34:14,239 --> 00:34:15,159
Don't you think so?

707
00:34:15,320 --> 00:34:16,519
If you're willing,

708
00:34:16,559 --> 00:34:17,760
help me drive for now.

709
00:34:18,000 --> 00:34:19,880
At least eight thousand a month.

710
00:34:20,239 --> 00:34:21,239
And don't think that's too little.

711
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:22,559
There are also bonuses.

712
00:34:24,119 --> 00:34:25,719
I'm fine with driving.

713
00:34:26,719 --> 00:34:27,840
Then just sign it.

714
00:34:27,840 --> 00:34:28,880
It has to go through the accounts.

715
00:34:28,960 --> 00:34:30,360
No, no, the contract isn't urgent.

716
00:34:30,840 --> 00:34:32,239
You can try it out for a while first.

717
00:34:33,199 --> 00:34:34,000
That works too.

718
00:34:35,320 --> 00:34:35,880
What are you doing?

719
00:34:35,880 --> 00:34:36,760
The keys.

720
00:34:38,039 --> 00:34:38,920
Where are you going?

721
00:34:40,239 --> 00:34:41,800
I'm going to get familiar with the car first.

722
00:34:42,639 --> 00:34:43,800
So I don't end up crashing it later.

723
00:34:44,000 --> 00:34:44,599
You...

724
00:34:44,960 --> 00:34:45,920
Alright, alright, let's go.

725
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:46,880
Okay, Mr. Li.

726
00:34:46,880 --> 00:34:48,880
Call Xiao Yueyue over for me.

727
00:34:48,880 --> 00:34:49,599
Okay, Mr. Li.

728
00:34:49,599 --> 00:34:50,519
Close the door.

729
00:34:53,920 --> 00:34:54,519
Sir,

730
00:34:54,519 --> 00:34:56,679
I want to take my dog to the crematorium for cremation.

731
00:34:56,679 --> 00:34:57,840
Could you please give me a ride, sir?

732
00:34:57,840 --> 00:34:59,199
A dead dog? No, no, no.

733
00:34:59,199 --> 00:35:00,920
I won't dirty your car.

734
00:35:01,239 --> 00:35:01,639
No, no.

735
00:35:01,639 --> 00:35:02,960
I'm begging you, sir, I'm begging you.

736
00:35:02,960 --> 00:35:05,000
Please give me a ride, I'm begging you, sir.

737
00:35:16,599 --> 00:35:19,199
Miss, do you have an urgent matter?

738
00:35:19,559 --> 00:35:20,360
Driver,

739
00:35:20,880 --> 00:35:23,360
I want to take my dog to the crematorium for cremation.

740
00:35:23,679 --> 00:35:25,480
Is it okay if I hold it while getting in your car?

741
00:35:25,480 --> 00:35:26,159
It's fine, it's fine.

742
00:35:26,159 --> 00:35:27,239
Get in, I'll take you there.

743
00:35:27,239 --> 00:35:28,159
Thank you, driver.

744
00:35:28,159 --> 00:35:29,719
Sorry for the trouble, thank you, driver.

745
00:35:46,960 --> 00:35:47,760
Xiao Yueyue

746
00:35:48,440 --> 00:35:49,239
Xiao Yueyue

747
00:35:49,559 --> 00:35:51,440
Hey, hurry up and help me call a car.

748
00:35:52,039 --> 00:35:52,760
Boss

749
00:35:52,760 --> 00:35:54,840
Didn't you ask Brother Ming to be your driver?

750
00:35:54,880 --> 00:35:55,920
He's not my driver.

751
00:35:55,920 --> 00:35:57,079
That's my dad.

752
00:35:57,800 --> 00:35:58,719
Hello, hello, hello

753
00:36:00,079 --> 00:36:01,880
Brother Liu, Brother Liu, I—

754
00:36:02,239 --> 00:36:04,079
I'm almost there, just two more traffic lights.

755
00:36:05,880 --> 00:36:06,679
Alright, see you in a bit.

756
00:36:06,679 --> 00:36:07,599
Right away, right away.

757
00:36:15,280 --> 00:36:16,079
Thank you.

758
00:36:18,119 --> 00:36:19,280
Was it sick?

759
00:36:20,119 --> 00:36:20,760
No.

760
00:36:23,079 --> 00:36:24,440
It was just too old.

761
00:36:25,119 --> 00:36:27,320
It couldn't eat and couldn't stand anymore.

762
00:36:27,320 --> 00:36:28,519
It even developed bedsores.

763
00:36:28,760 --> 00:36:29,599
The doctor said

764
00:36:30,079 --> 00:36:32,480
if it kept going, it would just suffer more.

765
00:36:33,320 --> 00:36:35,039
So I had it put to sleep.

766
00:36:36,559 --> 00:36:37,400
How old was it?

767
00:36:37,840 --> 00:36:39,039
Fourteen years old.

768
00:36:39,400 --> 00:36:42,480
That's over a hundred in human years.

769
00:36:42,960 --> 00:36:44,039
It's considered a happy passing.

770
00:36:51,840 --> 00:36:52,440
Miss

771
00:36:53,039 --> 00:36:55,519
If you're feeling upset, just let yourself cry.

772
00:36:56,000 --> 00:36:56,880
Don't hold it in.

773
00:37:12,960 --> 00:37:14,400
Here, have some water.

774
00:37:16,039 --> 00:37:16,840
Thank you.

775
00:37:27,039 --> 00:37:28,199
From now on,

776
00:37:28,880 --> 00:37:30,119
don't just drink water without checking.

777
00:37:30,239 --> 00:37:31,239
And don't get in as soon as the door opens.

778
00:37:32,360 --> 00:37:34,000
If you take a ride with a stranger,

779
00:37:34,480 --> 00:37:36,679
you should write down the license plate number.

780
00:37:36,719 --> 00:37:38,639
Send it to your friends or family as a precaution.

781
00:37:38,639 --> 00:37:39,440
Otherwise,

782
00:37:39,519 --> 00:37:41,000
you could easily run into danger.

783
00:37:42,719 --> 00:37:46,119
Why do you sound so much like a police officer?

784
00:37:49,199 --> 00:37:50,280
I think so too.

785
00:37:52,440 --> 00:37:53,239
Sir,

786
00:37:54,400 --> 00:37:57,079
do you think there's reincarnation in this world?

787
00:37:59,239 --> 00:38:01,280
I hope it can be my dog again in the next life.

788
00:38:03,639 --> 00:38:04,440
It's hard to say.

789
00:38:05,880 --> 00:38:07,039
I hope so too.

790
00:38:08,360 --> 00:38:09,639
If it really exists,

791
00:38:11,159 --> 00:38:12,440
All these bad people

792
00:38:12,760 --> 00:38:14,239
should be treated like animals.

793
00:38:14,880 --> 00:38:16,480
Only good people deserve to be called human.

794
00:38:17,840 --> 00:38:18,639
If that's the case,

795
00:38:20,239 --> 00:38:22,000
there would be no more crime in the future.

796
00:38:22,840 --> 00:38:24,400
And there would be no need for police.

797
00:38:24,559 --> 00:38:27,400
Are bad deeds really only done by bad people?

798
00:38:52,599 --> 00:38:53,400
Is it here?

799
00:38:53,599 --> 00:38:54,400
Yes, yes.

800
00:38:54,480 --> 00:38:55,400
Excuse me, sir.

801
00:38:55,880 --> 00:38:56,960
How much is it? I'll pay you.

802
00:38:56,960 --> 00:38:57,760
No need, no need.

803
00:38:58,119 --> 00:38:59,840
You really thought I was an unlicensed driver.

804
00:39:01,360 --> 00:39:04,360
I was just out for a drive because I had nothing to do.

805
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:06,880
I should thank you for keeping me company.

806
00:39:08,679 --> 00:39:09,679
Thank you, sir.

807
00:39:10,079 --> 00:39:11,039
Sorry to trouble you.

808
00:40:13,920 --> 00:40:15,159
I've been searching for a long time.

809
00:42:07,440 --> 00:42:08,239
Thank you.

810
00:42:18,840 --> 00:42:20,760
Don't act silly all day, understand?

811
00:42:20,760 --> 00:42:21,440
You're already an adult.

812
00:42:21,440 --> 00:42:22,559
No problem, big bro.

813
00:42:27,519 --> 00:42:29,280
I'll leave everything about those two to you from now on.

814
00:42:29,280 --> 00:42:29,679
Okay.

815
00:42:29,960 --> 00:42:30,639
Don't worry, big brother.

816
00:42:31,480 --> 00:42:32,159
Leave it to me.

817
00:42:47,679 --> 00:42:48,239
Big Brother Dali

818
00:42:48,880 --> 00:42:51,079
What do you mean? Weren't you suspended?

819
00:42:51,480 --> 00:42:52,639
Did you get the photo?

820
00:42:52,639 --> 00:42:53,239
I got it.

821
00:42:53,239 --> 00:42:54,079
Check it quickly.

822
00:42:54,079 --> 00:42:55,440
Is that person Sun Haixing?

823
00:42:56,559 --> 00:42:57,800
Yes. Where are you?

824
00:42:58,000 --> 00:42:58,960
Are you sure?

825
00:42:59,320 --> 00:43:00,000
I'm sure.

826
00:43:00,000 --> 00:43:01,880
I'm at Qian Ferry in Ancheng.

827
00:43:02,199 --> 00:43:04,360
Notify the local police right away.
